3.3 PLOTTING
We generate figures from the synthesized source data using the open-source plotting library Bokeh. Bokeh was selected for its ease of use and modification and its expressiveness. We modified the
5 In the sense of strictly greater/less than. This clarification is provided to judges for the human baseline.

