cantly outperforms the simpler CNN+LSTM model. Our human baseline shows that the problem is challenging, but leads by a significant margin.
Tables 4 and 5 show the performances of the RN and our editorial staff per figure type and per question type, respectively. More details on the human baseline and an analysis of results are provided in the supplementary material.
